{"word":"γνῶμα","slug":"γνῶμα","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<el><b>γνῶμα</b></el> <br/><b><a href='S:Etymology'>Etym.</a> </b><a href='S:γιγνώσκω'><el>γιγνώσκω</el></a>\n<p/><div class='li500'><b>I. </b><i>a mark, token</i>, like <el>γνώρισμα</el>, <b><a href='S:Herodotus'>Hdt.</a></b>, <b><a href='S:Sophocles'>Soph.</a></b><p/></div><div class='li500'><b>II. </b><i>an opinion, judgment</i>, = <a href='S:γνώμη'><el>γνώμη</el></a>, <b><a href='S:Aeschylus'>Aesch.</a></b>, <b><a href='S:Euripides'>Eur.</a></b><p/></div>"}]}